  [Electric heating mantle with variable control — 250ml or 500ml], [1], [Preferred over open flame for Year One. Variable temperature essential.],
  [Water bath (bain-marie) or electric hot plate], [1], [For gentle extraction and digestion work. A glass bain-marie on a hotplate is acceptable.],
  [Laboratory thermometer — 0°C to 150°C minimum], [1], [Non-negotiable for distillation. Mercury-free preferred.],
  [Infrared (non-contact) thermometer], [1], [For monitoring calcination temperature without contact. Critical for the 400°C limit.],
  [Ring stand with iron rings and clamps], [1], [For supporting flasks during distillation and heating.],
  [Wire gauze pad], [2], [Protects glass from direct flame if open burner is used.],
)

